/target/

# Backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# If you are building a Rust library, you generally ignore Cargo.lock. 
# If you are building a binary/app, you should commit Cargo.lock. 
# Uncomment the next line if you want to ignore it:
# Cargo.lock

